  <description>
    <p>Completely rewritten to accomodate new features and to be even speedier, Open TV has been carefully crafted to deliver the best IPTV experience</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Import your IPTV channels from any source (M3U File, M3U link, Xtream) 🗃️</li>
      <li>Record while watching 🎥</li>
      <li>Multi IPTV sources 🎊</li>
      <li>Control the UI from a TV remote 📺</li>
      <li>Super low ram usage, crazy speeds and instant search 🚅</li>
      <li>Refresh your sources when you need it 🔄</li>
      <li>Add channels to favorites 🌟</li>
    </ul>
    <p>PLEASE consider donating, I've been developing this app solo for the past 2 years! Instructions on my github (https://github.com/Fredolx/open-tv)</p>
  </description>
